<html>

<head>
  <title>
    Billing - TheGestor
  </title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <style>
    .image {
      display: block;
      margin-right: auto;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-top: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      height: 350px;
      width: 300px;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .text {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      margin-top: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.56);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: normal;
      padding: 10px;
    }

    .block {
      display: block;
      margin: auto;
      width: 300px;
      border: none;
      background-color: #3195b1;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      font-size: 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0px 2px 2px 2px #bdbdbd;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {
      .text {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
      }

      .block {
        width: 20rem;
        padding: 1rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <form name="from" action="<%- url %>" method="POST">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col">
          <img class="image" src="https://thegestor-data.s3.amazonaws.com/views/GRAPHIC+001.svg" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col">
          <p class="text-center">
            Al hacer clic en aceptar estás de acuerdo con TheGestor<br />
            <a href="https://thegestor.com/privacy-policy-es/" target="_blank">Política de privacidad</a> y los <a
              href="https://thegestor.com/terms-and-conditions-es/" target="_blank">Términos y Condiciones</a><br />
            Este pago será recurrente hasta que el usuario cancele la suscripción.<br />
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col">
          <input type="hidden" name="Ds_SignatureVersion" value="<%- Ds_SignatureVersion %>" />
          <input type="hidden" name="Ds_MerchantParameters" value="<%- Ds_MerchantParameters %>" />
          <input type="hidden" name="Ds_Signature" value="<%- Ds_Signature %>" />
          <input type="submit" value="Aceptar y continuar" class="btn block">
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>
  </form>
</body>

</html>